data.description: Great property located in the highly desirable Jenks school district. This home has it all. From curb appeal to the inside features this property is one to show. This 3 bedroom/1.5 bath house has all the comforts of home. It is a first-time homebuyers dream at an amazing price point with all appliances included. Windows come with a lifetime transferrable warranty, Exterior painting done 2023. Garage door opener has backup battery that allows it to be opened during power outages. The neighborhood is a short distance to HWY 75 which can get you all over town. Neighbors are awesome which is a plus.
